The paper proposes a new framework for common and individual feature extraction from multiblock data, which involves dimensionality reduction and blind source separation techniques. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories, including machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), signal processing (cs.SI), and information theory (cs.IT).
